query:
UPDATE island_guides ig
JOIN places p ON ig.name = p.name
JOIN atolls a ON p.atollId = a.id AND a.name = ig.atoll
SET ig.placeId = p.id
WHERE ig.contentType = 'island' AND ig.placeId IS NULL
